The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Aperitivo has the edge 

 STAR RACER

 Calcutta: There is little to choose between Aperitivo and Moon Forest in the 2,000m Indian Champion Cup, the main event in Tuesdays card.

 If Aperitivo is one of the best old horses in the country, Moon Forest was an easy winner of the Derby, earlier this month. However, the trainer-jockey duo of Vijay Singh and C.Rajendra is riding high on luck. Aperitivo, therefore, may just about score. 

